This is a collection of shell (Bash) scripts which main purpose is to manage
Amazon EC2 instances through simple CLI interface. The basic implemented tasks
are: automated backup with help of cron utility and manual restore with help of
the menu-driven system.

But remember the backups are not guaranteed to be consistent. This tools were
initially designed to backup/recovery of the outstaff deveploper machines and
must not be used for Database/Transactional and other servers.
